snippet.title: Official Fix-it-up 80s: Meet Kate's Parents HD Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Take a trip back to the 80's in this totally tubular, time management adventure!

Kate visits her father and he explains how the family got its start in the auto repair biz.

Play as Kate's parents, Frank and Mary, to purchase, fix, paint, rent, and sell cars in seven exciting locations.

Cash in on tailoring car design to customers' needs, expand the business, hire more employees to pimp the rides and make them glow.

Experience the thrill of success more than ever before in Fix-it-Up 80's: Meet Kate's Parents!

Features:

- 45 Levels and 7 Free Play levels
- 7 Unique locations
- 10 Types of cars and 6 emergency vehicles to fix
- Hire employees and train them
- Upgrades, achievements and more!
- Game Center Support
- iOS 4+ multitasking support

iTunes Store Page:

http://itunes.apple.com/nz/app/fix-it-up-80s-meet-kates-parents/id494879092?mt=8

Homepage:

http://www.g5e.com/games/fix_it_up_80s_ipad
